---
title: Steak & Green Pepper Quesadillas with Hot Sauce & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: Cheesy, crispy, and stuffed with delectable delights, quesadillas are one of our all-time favorite easy dinners. In fact, if left to our own devices, we could probably eat them every night of the week (and may have done so once or twice). Here, tortillas are layered with not one, but TWO types of cheese, plus zesty spiced steak and sautéed green pepper. They toast up in the pan until gooey on the inside and golden outside—the perfect pairing for a dollop of smoky red pepper crema and a dash of hot sauce. Try to top that!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-green-pepper-quesadillas-98636bb4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/steak-green-pepper-quesadillas-5ea8310a56a9d32f9d717bc9-600ac602.pdf
cuisine: Mexican
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/steak-and-green-pepper-quesadillas-5ea8310a56a9d32f9d717bc9
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
  fat: 42 g
  saturated fat: 20 g
